Our client is an award-winning market leader in manufacturing operating offices across the world. To cope with the expansion of the business, they are seeking for a high-caliber individual to join their expanding team.

Job Responsibilities: 

Responsible for managing project development from design stage to mass production, handling product cost evaluation,
Performing feasibility study.
Supervise Engineering Team, resource & job arrangement for the project team.

Job Requirements:

Higher Diploma/Degree in Manufacturing, Mechanical, Electronic , Industrial Engineering or related;
At least 3 year experience in OEM/ODM product development & project follow-up with consumer product manufacturing company;
Strong product design and construction senses;
Good knowledge of 3D program and AutoCAD; 
Mature, independent, analytical mind and under pressure;
Good command of spoken & written English & Mandarin.

崗位要求:
大學學位，自然科學或工程系畢業者優先考慮
擁有 5 - 6 年市場經驗
熟悉亞洲地區銷售及市場文化
熟悉電子市場媒體及銷售
操流利英語及普通話
必須願意公幹

工作範圍及職責:


管理及協調市場部的工作，以達致公司目標;
維繫客戶長久之關係;
處理公司隨時安排之計劃;
應徵者必須提供短片，包括自我介紹及如何提升職位的價值;
應徵者必須提供新冠疫苗注射證書 (如因健康理由，懷孕不適宜注射除外)。

Responsibilities

Provide first level technical support to office users in a timely manner;
Perform troubleshooting and quality tape management;
Support daily IT operations, e.g. system maintenance including MS Windows servers, Active Directory, MS Exchange, firewall, router and network monitoring, etc.
Maintenance of all hardware and software inventory control
Provide helpdesk support, technical services and daily routine task and system operation;
Handle/analyst in-house system and/or program;
Liaise with external providers of hardware and software to resolves IT issues
Carry out other ad-hoc assignments
Requirement

Diploma or above in Information Technology related discipline or equivalent experience
3 years' experience in providing helpdesk / IT support / back office operations
Strong sense of analytical and problem solving skills;
The ability to work independently, coordinate others to accomplish overall corporate goals and deal with business users at all levels;
Excellent Communication and interpersonal skills;
Positive thinking, hardworking, responsible, Independent, attentive to details, initiative, with good communication, strong problem-solving, analytical and interpersonal skills
Ability to multi-task and work in a fast paced environment to meet daily goals and willing to work overtime and outdoor work occasionally
Immediate available is an advantage
Interested parties please go to www.okia.com for more details, and send full resume, current and expected salary to us.

Key Responsibilities:

Preparing documents (e.g. MBPR & SOPs) and reports;
Organize production schedule to ensure smooth and efficient production operations;
Supervise and monitor day-to-day running of the production operation;
Coordinate with other departments on production schedule and validation arrangement;
Perform routine check in the Production Department to ensure GMP implementation and compliance;
Provide technical support and trouble shooting.

Requirements:

Higher Diploma or above in Pharmaceutical Sciences or any related Sciences Studies;
Good command of both spoken and written English and Chinese.
Proficient in MS Office application (Excel, Word & PowerPoint) and Chinese Word Processing;
Recent graduates will be considered;
Immediate available is highly preferable;
Fresh graduates are welcomed.

 How to Apply

You are invited to send in your application and CV stating the position (with reference number) you are applying for together with your current and expected salary, either by "Apply Now" or mail to Rm 5-6, 9/F, Block B, Vigor Industrial Building, 14-20 Cheung Tat Road, Tsing Yi on or before 31 May 2021.

Marching Pharmaceutical Limited is an Equal Opportunities Employer. Personal data provided by job applicants will be used strictly in accordance with our personal data policy and for recruitment purposes only. We aim to respond to successful applicants within 8 weeks and related information will be kept in our file for up to 12 months for other suitable vacancies in our organization and thereafter destroyed.
